63 class QuadrotorDecoupled6DRelPlanarDubins3D
64  : public RelativeDynamics<PositionVelocity, QuadrotorControl,
65  PlanarDubins3D, double> {
66 public:
67  ~QuadrotorDecoupled6DRelPlanarDubins3D() {}
68  explicit QuadrotorDecoupled6DRelPlanarDubins3D()
69  : RelativeDynamics<PositionVelocity, QuadrotorControl, PlanarDubins3D,
70  double>() {}
71 
72  // Derived classes must be able to give the time derivative of relative state
73  // as a function of current state and control of each system.
74  inline std::unique_ptr<RelativeState<PositionVelocity, PlanarDubins3D>>
75  Evaluate(const PositionVelocity &tracker_x, const QuadrotorControl &tracker_u,
76  const PlanarDubins3D &planner_x, const double &planner_u) const {
77  // Compute relative state.
78  const PositionVelocityRelPlanarDubins3D relative_x(tracker_x, planner_x);
79 
80  // TODO(@jaime): Check these calculations.
81  // Relative distance derivative.
82  distance_dot =
83  relative_x.TangentVelocity() * std::cos(relative_x.Bearing()) +
84  relative_x.NormalVelocity() * std::sin(relative_x.Bearing());
85 
86  // Relative bearing derivative.
87  bearing_dot =
88  -planner_u -
89  relative_x.TangentVelocity() * std::sin(relative_x.Bearing()) +
90  relative_x.NormalVelocity() * std::cos(relative_x.Bearing());
91 
92  // Relative tangent and normal velocity derivatives.
93  // NOTE! Must rotate roll/pitch into planner frame.
94  const double c = std::cos(planner_x.Theta());
95  const double s = std::sin(planner_x.Theta());
96 
97  tangent_velocity_dot = tracker_u.pitch * c - tracker_u.roll * s +
98  planner_u * relative_x.TangentVelocity();
99  normal_velocity_dot = -tracker_u.pitch * s - tracker_u.roll * c -
100  planner_u * relative_x.TangentVelocity();
101 
102  return std::unique_ptr<PositionVelocityRelPlanarDubins3D>(
103  new PositionVelocityRelPlanarDubins3D() distance_dot, bearing_dot,
104  tangent_velocity_dot, normal_velocity_dot));
105  }
106

109  // by the given system states, provided abstract control bounds.

112  const RelativeState<PositionVelocity, PlanarDubins3D> &value_gradient,
113  const QuadrotorControlBoundCylinder &tracker_u_bound,
114  const ScalarBoundInterval &planner_u_bound) const {
115  // TODO(@dfk, @jaime): figure this part out.
116  }
